itunes:title: Listen to this when you need a friend to talk to
title: Listen to this when you need a friend to talk to
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
description:
this is just a chat! I feel like we all need a chat. Not like anything special but just to chat like old pals and that's what you and me are! So I hope you enjoy this one and it can turn the world off for 30 mins for you
